---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy policy for Montessori-Kinderhaus Potsdam West." locale="en">
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 px-4 md:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold mb-8">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Responsible Body</h2>

        <address class="not-italic mb-6 text-text-muted">
          <strong class="text-text">Montessori-Kinderhaus Potsdam e.V.</strong><br />
          Knobelsdorffstr. 7<br />
          14471 Potsdam<br /><br />
          Phone: 0331 â€“ 620 44 30<br />
          Email: info@mkiha.de
        </address>

        <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">Data Protection Officer</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted mb-6">
          Carolin Bollien<br />
          Email: datenschutz@mkiha.de
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Collection and Storage of Personal Data</h2>

        <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">Automatic Data Collection</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted mb-4">
          When you visit our website, technical information is automatically collected:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-muted mb-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Browser type and version</li>
          <li>Operating system used</li>
          <li>Referrer URL</li>
          <li>IP address</li>
          <li>Time of server request</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">Contacting Us</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted mb-6">
          When you contact us by email, phone or contact form, your details are stored to process the enquiry. Processing is based on contract fulfilment or our legitimate interests.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Cookies</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted mb-6">
          This website uses cookies. You can configure your browser to inform you about the setting of cookies and to allow cookies only on a case-by-case basis, to exclude the acceptance of cookies for certain cases or in general, and to activate the automatic deletion of cookies when closing the browser.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted mb-4">
          Under the GDPR you have the following rights:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-muted mb-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Right of access to your stored personal data</li>
          <li>Right to rectification of inaccurate data</li>
          <li>Right to erasure of your data</li>
          <li>Right to restriction of processing</li>
          <li>Right to data portability</li>
          <li>Right to object to processing (Art. 21 GDPR)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Google Maps</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted mb-6">
          We use Google Maps on our website to display our location. When using Google Maps, data is transferred to Google servers in the USA. For more information, please see Google's privacy policy.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Right to Complain</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted mb-6">
          You have the right to complain to a data protection supervisory authority about the processing of your personal data.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
